Olu Jacobs, one of Nollywood’s most celebrated actors, is 77 years old today. As expected, many fans have sent him congratulatory messages on social media. One of those who celebrated him, is his wife, Joke Silva. The actress wrote him some loving words, wishing him a happy birthday on Instagram. Sharing photos of him, she wrote: “PRAISE THE LORD… Happy 77th birthday Sir J. May your days be long in good health and abundance.. The Quintisential Ovorawen. Loads of love King of my heart.” Source